description:
So, here it is, my first ever fully processed deep sky astrophotography image, NGC6188 (Fighting Dragons Of Ara) in SHO (Hubble Palette).

Captured  from the backyard over the course of several nights (02/07/2020, 03/07/2020, 05/07/2020, 07/07/2020, 10/07/2020. 11/07/2020 & 15/07/2020) this image consists of:

SII - 30 x 600s Unity Gain 111 Offset 0 Bin 1x1 -15C
Ha - 59 X 600s Unity Gain 111 Offset 0 Bin 1x1 -15C
